==Description==

The '''Std FreeCADForum''' command opens the FreeCAD Forum in the system's default Internet browser. The command requires a working Internet connection.

Currently the command points to [https://forum.freecad.org https://forum.freecad.org].

==Usage==

# Select the {{MenuCommand|Help → [[Image:Std_FreeCADForum.svg|16px]] FreeCAD Forum}} option from the menu.


